high_descs: Turn around and go to the end of the dresser, on your right.
Pick up the watch, to the right of the cardboard box, on the dresser.
Turn to your left and go past the dresser, to the lamp in the left corner of the living room, across from you.
Turn on the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the living room lamp.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight and turn left to face the end of the white desk.
Pick the watch up off of the white desk.
Go straight then left to face the lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn the lamp on in the corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Turn the lamp on while holding the watch.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the door, the turn left to face the end of the tv stand
Pick up the watch that is sitting on the tv stand to the right of the box
Turn around and cross the room to the tall lamp that is on the left of the couch
anns.task_desc: Examine a watch under a tall lamp
